text:
Eiza González Reyna (; born 30 January 1990) is a Mexican actress and singer. She became famous for her role as Dolores "Lola" Valente in the Mexican musical telenovela "Lola...Érase una vez" (2007–2008).
González gained further fame in the American horror series ' (2014–2016). She is also known for her roles as Monica "Darling" Castello in the action crime movie "Baby Driver" (2017) and as Nyssiana in the cyberpunk action movie ' (2019).
